Class RestDispatchAsyncModule

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GinModule

    public class RestDispatchAsyncModule
extends AbstractDispatchAsyncModule
    An implementation of AbstractDispatchAsyncModule that uses REST calls.

    This gin module provides provides access to the RestDispatch singleton, which is used to make calls to the server over HTTP. This module requires:

    You must manually bind @RestApplicationPath to point to your server API root path.
